----------------------------------
Boxing and Unboxing

Boxing - process of converting primitive value into its object form

Unboxing - Process of converting object back to its primitive form

-----------------------------------------
Exception
---------
It is an event that occurs during the execution of program which distrupts the normal flow of execution

try,catch,finally,throw,throws


Customised exceptions are checked exceptions - user has to handle before executing the program.



































